            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a move action, a skrell can tap into their innate psychic power to cause their outline to shift and blur, making their exact positioning difficult to determine visually. The skrell gains concealment until they deactivate this ability with another move action. This is a mind-affecting effect that other skrells are immune to.",
